Generates all of the tentacles with the given parameters.

Author:
Adam Panzica
Parameters:
expFactThe exponential factor parameter used to calculate the radius of the tentacle
seedRadThe seed radius for the speed set
seedLengthThe seed length that was used to calculate the seed radius
numTentThe total number of tentacles in the speed set
resolutionThe resolution of the occupancy grid that the tentacles will be overlaid on
xDimThe length of the x-axis of the occupancy grid, in the positive x-direction and of the same units as resolution
yDimThe length of the y-axis of the occupancy grid, in the positive y-direction and of the same units as resolution
velocityThe velocity that the tentacle is to be traveled at
